        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公主在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "宫女甲、宫女乙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在内帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就请相见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宫女甲、宫女乙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公主娘娘有请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（费贞娥上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，将军。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公主。"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公主请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军万福。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈……妙吓，这一福，就酥了俺半边也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军乃盖世英雄，皇朝梁栋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不敢，拙夫不才，怎当公主称羡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴家乃亡国之女，不堪侍奉宫闱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢！公主乃金枝玉叶，凤女天孙，万望勿嫌愚夫鲁莽，万分之幸！今后内宫\n之事，悉听公主掌管。凡有吩咐，小将一一从命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，将军，夫妇乃人伦之始，当行花烛之礼，合卺之仪，方成大礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公主言之有理，仕女们撤宴过来，待俺与公主交拜天地！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖小开门〗。定席。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公主请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖曲牌收〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀，银台上好辉煌也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（脱布衫带叨叨令）银台上煌煌的凤烛燉，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金猊内袅袅的香烟喷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "和你一夜夫妻百夜恩。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "费贞娥 （脱布衫带叨叨令）恁道一夜夫妻百夜恩，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "试问恁三生石上可有良缘分？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还只怕漂漂渺渺的波涛滚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（脱布衫带叨叨令）恁道是乐煞人也么哥！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（脱布衫带叨叨令）又道是喜煞人也么哥！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "侍女们，看酒来，待俺回敬公主一杯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军所赐，奴家敢不从命？要请将军陪奴一大杯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公主要俺陪一大杯，当得的，仕女们斟酒！"
        },
        {
          "character": "宫女甲、宫女乙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公主请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "干！"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "干！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李过吐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（脱布衫带叨叨令）赤紧的蠢不剌沙叱利也学些丰和韵。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李过醉。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公主，俺醉得紧了，安寝了罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "侍女们辛苦了，将酒筵分散她们去罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也要留几个房中服侍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "房中自有奴家服侍，教她们去罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吖，想是公主怕羞，不好就寝。\n侍女们！"
        },
        {
          "character": "宫女甲、宫女乙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "过来谢了公主。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宫女甲、宫女乙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢公主娘娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "掌灯！"
        },
        {
          "character": "宫女甲、宫女乙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖小开门〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回避！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（宫女甲、宫女乙同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军今夜为何还穿此铠甲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不瞒公主说，一向在皇兄帐中护卫，提防奸细，日夜不能卸甲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如今天下已定，还虑什么奸细。况今宵乃百年喜日，岂可穿此不祥之服？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公主说得有理，俺正要把身子松动松动，俺唤侍女们来卸甲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓？"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待奴家亲与将军卸甲，才是妇道。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只是劳动不当。"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好说。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（脱布衫） 除下了铁兜鍪凤翅嶙峋，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "放下了宝龙泉偷看利刃。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卸下了𤠯猊铠锁子龙鳞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哇呀呀……"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军尊臂为何如此？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不瞒公主说，前日在宁武关被遇吉打了一鞭，至今尚未痊愈。哈哈痛死我也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来如此。请将军入帐安息罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公主也早些睡罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴家除了簪珥，脱了袍服就来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就来吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就来的。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（小梁州） 除下了翠翘宝髻耳珰瑱，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "脱却了凤衮龙氤氲。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "防滑褪紧拴起绣罗裙。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖起二更鼓〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（么篇） 听听房栊寂寂悄无人，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但闻得戍漏频频。"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军，将军呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（么篇） 我觑，觑着他眯奚醉眼醒还昏，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休惊盹，心窝内宝刀抡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贼子看刀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀。啊呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（么篇） 钢刀上冤气伸，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李过",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀，啊呀，呓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（么篇） 银灯下冤家殒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叹苍天不佑。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（么篇） 不能够把巨寇刃，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳，便、便死向泉台。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（宫女甲、宫女乙同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "宫女甲、宫女乙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "房中为何喧嚷？我们进去看来。吓，这是二大王，为何杀死在地？想是她刺死\n的，拿去见大王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哫，谁敢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "宫女甲、宫女乙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀，公主饶命㖸！"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我非公主。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宫女甲、宫女乙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我乃费氏宫人，杀此巨寇，与君父报仇。便将我凌迟碎剐，啊呀，也不畏惧的\n㖸！"
        },
        {
          "character": "宫女甲、宫女乙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大大王将你许配二大王也不辱没了你，亏你下此毒手！"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朝天子） 恁道谎阳台雨云，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可知俺女专诸不解江皋韵。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀，遇冤家难含忍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朝天子） 拚得个柳憔花翠，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可也珠残玉损。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀早难道贪恋荣华终天恨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宫女甲、宫女乙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拿你去见大大王就该死哩！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "费贞娥 （朝天子） 一任他碎骨粉身，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一任他扬灰碾尘！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日个含笑归泉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宫女甲、宫女乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀费贞娥吓费贞娥——"
        },
        {
          "character": "宫女甲、宫女乙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "她叫费贞娥！"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可惜你大才小用了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朝天子） 𠮾，又、又何必多磨吻。"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看此贼又活了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "宫女甲、宫女乙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "费贞娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀，罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（费贞娥自刎下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "宫女甲、宫女乙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀，她竟自刎了，我们将尸首抬过一旁，报与大大王知道。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "宫女甲、宫女乙",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三寸气在千般用，一旦无常万事休。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宫女甲、宫女乙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀，二大王吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（宫女甲、宫女乙同哭下。）"
        }
